The likely categories for this paper are:

1) Health & Personal Care - The paper is about a skincare product, which falls under the category of personal care.

2) Beauty - The paper specifically mentions skincare and improving complexion, which aligns with the beauty category.

3) Luxury Beauty - The paper mentions unique ingredients and targeted bio-brightening, which suggests a higher-end or luxury skincare product.

4) All Beauty - This category encompasses all beauty products, including skincare.

5) Beauty & Personal Care - This category combines both beauty and personal care products, which is relevant to the content of the paper.
